25
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:05,542
Please excuse me...

26
00:02:08,503 --> 00:02:10,088
<i>It's just as I thought.</i>

27
00:02:10,547 --> 00:02:13,008
<i>I also don't want the police
to know</i>

28
00:02:13,091 --> 00:02:16,345
<i>that I've come into contact
with an FBI agent.</i>

29
00:02:16,762 --> 00:02:19,681
<i>If my father ever found out,
he'd tell L.</i>

30
00:02:20,432 --> 00:02:22,601
<i>Raye doesn't suspect me at all...</i>

31
00:02:23,101 --> 00:02:25,979
<i>The police will deal with
what happened just now</i>

32
